      "name": "2 tablespoons butter",
      "amount": ""
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Place phyllo sheets on a clean surface and brush lightly with melted butter.",
    "Layer slices of cheddar cheese over the phyllo, then add thinly sliced cabbage. Brush with remaining butter.",
    "Fold sides inward to create a packet, sealing edges with additional phyllo if necessary.",
    "Bake for 25 minutes or until golden brown and crispy on top.",
    "Serve hot as a side dish or as a snack."
